OL,7,FThey're ecstatic. Scientists who
OL,8,Fbelieve in the potential of
OL,9,Fpsychedelic drugs to treat mental
OL,10,Fhealth problems are delighted to hear
OL,11,Fabout a new legal change in Australia.
OL,13,FThe country's medical regulator, the
OL,14,FTherapeutic Goods Administration
OL,15,F(TGA), has changed the rules so that
OL,16,FMDMA (ecstasy) can be used to treat
OL,17,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder, and
OL,18,Fpsilocybin (the active ingredient in
OL,19,Fmagic mushrooms) is available for
OL,20,F"treatment-resistant" depression.
OL,3,CWhy the UK should not follow
OL,4,CAustralia's legalisation of
OL,5,Cpsychedelics for mental health
